<p class="section-text">Now that Christmas is nearly upon us, it&#8217;s time to stock up on jet-setting essentials for escaping these dipping temperatures. The savviest of travelers not only know how to plan, but they also know how to pack. And since I can&#8217;t physically map out your trips and fill your suitcases, I crafted a shopping itinerary instead to help streamline the process for you.</p>
<p>Or, an incredibly curated gift-guide for the traveler in your life!</p>
