		<description><![CDATA[<p>This post is sponsored by Sephora. Tis the season, right? The season for shopping, holiday parties, total and complete exhaustion&#8230; &#8230;anyone else feeling this way? I think I&#8217;ve been to the mall 4 times in the past few days and it&#8217;s firming my resolve to not go near a mall the entire month of January!...</p>
