				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This post is sponsored by Sephora.</p>
<p>Tis the season, right? The season for shopping, holiday parties, total and complete exhaustion&#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230;anyone else feeling this way?</p>
<p>I think I&#8217;ve been to the mall 4 times in the past few days and it&#8217;s firming my resolve to not go near a mall the entire month of January! But one thing that has been fun has been getting stocking stuffers out of the way! Good things really do come in small packages and <a href="https://rstyle.me/+KmUMiMAdXp9HKYqs7o9p4g" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Sephora</a> is out to prove that this holiday season. They&#8217;ve put together a ton of <a href="https://rstyle.me/+dBoqEkysmxbzPFMW92spiw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">gift sets</a> in a bunch of categories like <a href="https://rstyle.me/+3bqdW1267fZ89mqDv4IOMg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">fragrance</a>, <a href="https://rstyle.me/+qz0iPMHZK3mg7CNytaSlWQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">makeup</a>, and <a href="https://rstyle.me/+KmUMiMAdXp9HKYqs7o9p4g" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">skincare</a>! You can snag a travel-size of your favorite products or something you’ve been meaning to try! But this year I&#8217;m taking advantage of their offerings and I grabbed a bunch of stocking stuffers for Emery and Anisten.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9306" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01517.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01517.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01517-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01517-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01517-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /></p>
<p class="css-a1jw00 " style="text-align: center;" data-comp="DisplayName Flex Box"><a href="https://rstyle.me/+sGnBI_xd5Sl3mtw50vPnKw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><span class="css-0">O.M.G. (Oh My Glow) BRIGHTENING SET</span></a></p>
<p>Ok, I <em>may</em> have grabbed a few for myself as well. And I&#8217;m kind of dying to show them to you guys! They&#8217;re some of my FAVORITE products and because they&#8217;re in gift sets, they&#8217;re also serving up major savings! So I rounded up a few of my must-have tiny-sized products and miniature sets from brands like <a href="https://rstyle.me/+FqcjRl41Q0j7bbDCC7CmNw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Fresh</a>, <a href="https://rstyle.me/+0sBK5bfygLVzoD_jpIE0kg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Laniege</a>, <a href="https://rstyle.me/+XLNAHs_YfGeLebhQpu7new" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Tatcha</a>, and more that you should definitely snag before they (inevitably) go out of stock!</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-9302 aligncenter" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01526.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01526.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01526-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01526-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01526-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://rstyle.me/+fLq6lOPC7oyu8s9Whjl1qA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">FRESH SUGAR LIPS GIFT SET</a></p>
<h3 class="css-a1jw00 " data-comp="DisplayName Flex Box"><strong><a href="https://rstyle.me/+fLq6lOPC7oyu8s9Whjl1qA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><span class="css-0">Sugar Lip Legends Gift Set</span></a></strong></h3>
<p><em>Fresh</em></p>
<p>This gift set is $42 (<em>$74 value</em>), but the feeling of nourished, non-chapped lips during the winter is pretty much priceless. My girls are a bit past the stage of the dollar chapsticks that come in a pack of 10. They want something that <em>actually</em> keeps their lips smooth and provides a bit of color without going full-on lipstick! They get the cult-favorite Sugar Lip Treatment Advanced Therapy and can then top it off with a subtle nude, pretty pink, or bright tint!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>SHOP ALL MY HOLIDAY GIFT SET PICKS</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><div class="shopthepost-widget" data-widget-id="3845073">
                <script type="text/javascript" language="javascript">
                    !function(d,s,id){
                        var e, p = /^http:/.test(d.location) ? 'http' : 'https';
                        if(!d.getElementById(id)) {
                            e     = d.createElement(s);
                            e.id  = id;
                            e.src = p + '://widgets.rewardstyle.com/js/shopthepost.js';
                            d.body.appendChild(e);
                        }
                        if(typeof window.__stp === 'object') if(d.readyState === 'complete') {
                            window.__stp.init();
                        }
                    }(document, 'script', 'shopthepost-script');
                </script>
                <div class="rs-adblock">
                    <img src="//assets.rewardstyle.com/images/search/350.gif" style="width:15px;height:15px;" onerror="this.parentNode.innerHTML='Turn off your ad blocker to view content'" />
                    <noscript>Turn on your JavaScript to view content</noscript>
                </div>
            </div></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">• • •</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9304" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01515.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01515.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01515-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01515-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01515-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://rstyle.me/+sGnBI_xd5Sl3mtw50vPnKw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><span class="css-0">O.M.G. (Oh My Glow) BRIGHTENING SET</span></a></p>
<h3><strong><a href="https://rstyle.me/+sGnBI_xd5Sl3mtw50vPnKw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><span class="css-0">O.M.G. (Oh My Glow) BRIGHTENING SET</span></a></strong></h3>
<p><em>Ole Henriksen</em></p>
<p>When Ole Henriksen launched Banana Bright Eye Crème, it sold out pretty much immediately. And every time it goes on sale or Sephora has a Beauty Insider event, it&#8217;s usually one of the first things to go out-of-stock. So I&#8217;m super pumped to try the rest of the products in this amazing kit! For $50 (<em>$98 value</em>), not only are you getting the famous undereye cream, but you&#8217;re also getting the Truth Serum®, C-Rush<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Brightening Gel Crème, and Banana Bright Face Primer!</p>
<div class="flex_row col-2"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9310" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01519.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01519.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01519-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01519-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01519-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9303" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01522.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01522.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01522-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01522-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01522-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /></div>
<p>Truth Serum®, formulated with True-C Complex<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> and collagen, helps brighten and firm skin. C-Rush<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Brightening Gel Crème, loaded with three sources of vitamin C and rose of winter extract, is supposed to pack in the hydration and target fine lines and wrinkles. Banana Bright<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Eye Crème, hydrates and lightens the undereye while the Vitamin-C powered Banana Bright<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Face Primer improves and extends makeup wear all day while delivering skincare benefits, too. It&#8217;s the kit that is made to help you glow!</p>
<h3><a href="https://rstyle.me/+KhDGJbrTGin0QB9LCvLewg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><strong>Being a Beauty Insider</strong></a></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Speaking of Sephora&#8217;s </span><a href="https://rstyle.me/+KhDGJbrTGin0QB9LCvLewg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Beauty Insider loyalty program</span></a>, if you haven&#8217;t joined yet, you definitely should!<span style="font-weight: 400;"> The program features three tiers based on your yearly Sephora spending — </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Beauty </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Insider, which is free, VIB if you spend at least $350, and Rouge if you spend $1,000 or more — with varying perks. </span></p>
<p><img class="size-large wp-image-6430 aligncenter" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Untitled-design-1-768x1024.png" alt="" width="640" height="853" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Untitled-design-1-768x1024.png 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Untitled-design-1-225x300.png 225w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re not already a Sephora Beauty Insider member, take a quick second and check out the perks and sign up </span><a href="https://rstyle.me/n/c8bni6benw7"><span style="font-weight: 400;">here</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> (totally worth it and also totally free!)</span></p>
<p>And once you&#8217;ve signed up, you need to check out my third pick for the PERFECT stocking stuffer!</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-9305 aligncenter" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01506.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01506.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01506-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01506-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01506-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://rstyle.me/+V-cJuKZF4TDYjz0LY6Brrw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">LIP GLOWY BALM KIT</a></p>
<h3 class="css-a1jw00 " data-comp="DisplayName Flex Box"><a href="https://rstyle.me/+V-cJuKZF4TDYjz0LY6Brrw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><strong><span class="css-0">Kiss Me All Day</span></strong></a></h3>
<p><em>Laneige</em></p>
<p>Not gonna lie, I was probably most excited when I saw this kit. I have been a die-hard fan of the <a href="https://rstyle.me/+YSaPkv5yhYAD1f-8VK0iog" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Laneige Lip Sleeping Mask</a> FOR-E-VER and when they brought out these Lip Glowy Balms I became an instant fan! When I first tried this trio — which are basically heaven and velvet and amazingness in a tube — I knew on the spot that they would have a place in my purse, car, bathroom, junk drawer, and anywhere else I decided to stash them. For starters, they smell <em>sublime! F</em>ormulated with murumuru and shea butter, each fruity-flavored tube can be used on-the-go for lips that are soft, smooth, and ready to conquer the day.</p>
<p><div class="flex_row col-2"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9308" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01507.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01507.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01507-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01507-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01507-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9311" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01514.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01514.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01514-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01514-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01514-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></div> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9309" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01494.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01494.jpg 6000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01494-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01494-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/DSC01494-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>At $35 (<em>$45 value</em>) for the set, these are the perfect lip balms for my girl&#8217;s stockings! Honestly, though, I scored with everything I purchased + I saved a ton!</p>
<p>Make sure you check out Sephora&#8217;s Beauty Insider loyalty program and then head to Sephora to shop for their incredible selection of gift kits! And then come back here and tell me what you pick up!</p>
<p>Happy Holidays!</p>
<p>Xx Tara</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://tarathueson.com/stocking-stuffers-w-sephora/">Stocking Stuffers w/ Sephora</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://tarathueson.com">Tara Thueson</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
