				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="p1">Ok, I have had this in the works for a while and I&#8217;m shocked I made it to today!</p>
<p class="p1">I have had the hardest time keeping this huge sale a secret! But I was able to swing it so that the <strong>ENTIRE</strong> Shine Cosmetics website is 20% off PLUS, we made some FUN bundles of my favorite things and the discount is even better with those! I have a discount code for you at the bottom of the post.</p>
<p class="p1">WHAT?!?!</p>
<p class="p1">Yes. That&#8217;s how I roll. I like my friends and I like to do nice things for my friends! So when Shine asked if there was something special I wanted to do for them, I said, &#8220;Yeah! Give &#8217;em a major discount!&#8221;</p>
<p class="p1">And they did!</p>
<p class="p1">I mean, I know people listen to me but I&#8217;m ALWAYS surprised when they do haha!</p>
<p>If you aren&#8217;t the blog reading type, I am going to make it easy for you! Click on the links below to grab your BUNDLES! Don&#8217;t forget to use code TARA at checkout to get an additional 10% off!</p>
