<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://shinecosmetics.com/collections/tara-thueson/products/taras-full-face-bundle?variant=31405582614564&amp;afmc=52t" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">FULL FACE BUNDLE (regular price $158 ON SALE for $100!)</a> | Use code TARA</p>
