				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: left;">With new cleansers, creams, masks, and moisturizers coming out daily, the competition is fierce for space on your bathroom sink. But the real tie-breaker? What works for YOUR skin. And if you&#8217;re been here for any amount of time, you know that what has worked for mine the past 18 months has been <a href="https://rstyle.me/+SSV1srfP1Gnl3XL7AYHPow" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">TULA Skincare.</a></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9180" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804.jpg 6000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://rstyle.me/+7kMq3EDAexX6chjZ15wIWg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">GLOW ALL OUT KIT</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Like you, I&#8217;ve swiped on, slathered, and pat on dozens of skin-care products in my lifetime. I&#8217;ve scrubbed with some pretty spectacular (and at times maybe not so great) exfoliators, tapped on too many eye creams to count, and peeled with the best of them to find something that really worked for my skin.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Even now, when I&#8217;m in deep winter denial, I still pull out the big guns to keep my face moisturized and my skin from chafing. I refuse to dig out my <em>real </em>cold-weather gear (you know, the <em>coat coat</em>) and I&#8217;m leaving my beanie and gloves in my closet for now. I usually hibernate this time of year because I prefer to stay warm but the weather has the opposite effect on my skin! Between being repeatedly hammered in the face with arctic wind and having all the moisture sucked out of the air, my skin, unfortunately, pays the price. But with my line-up, I&#8217;m going to show you just how I keep my skin in check!</p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://rstyle.me/+S9ChQFiFGB1OuzmHAzGL5g" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><strong>2 Staples You Need</strong></a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">For the health of my skin, I really do rely on the basics. And it doesn&#8217;t get more basic than a good cleanser. When I was younger, I thought that a good cleanser would leave my skin tight and squeaky clean. But now that I&#8217;m older and wiser, I know that this just isn&#8217;t good for my skin! A gentle cleanser, one that removes dirt and impurities but doesn&#8217;t strip the skin of its natural oils, is so important!</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">TULA&#8217;s <a href="https://rstyle.me/+jucEuGMfnczYyt-3dcbA1g" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Purifying Gel Cleanser</a> is so gentle and I use it with my favorite tool for washing my face, the <a href="https://rstyle.me/n/dc4svbbenw7" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Clarisonic brush</a>. The technology provides a deep cleanse that you can&#8217;t get with your hands. It&#8217;s a must for home use if you want that &#8216;fresh-from-my-esthetician&#8217; glow. I like to put a nickel-size amount of <a href="https://rstyle.me/+IgTmIiIVHFhr9pI_H6L8Tg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">the cleanser</a> on my brush and go to town!</p>
<div class="flex_row col-2"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9173" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09809.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09809.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09809-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09809-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09809-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9171" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09798.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09798.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09798-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09798-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09798-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></div>
<p>The other star in this duo is TULA&#8217;s cult-favorite <a href="https://rstyle.me/+R1mQfPkvyNKesHIf2hJAyg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Hydrating Day &amp; Night Cream</a>. Moisturizers are like Saran wrap for your skin—they lock in dampness to keep you hydrated and glowing. And this <a href="https://rstyle.me/+R1mQfPkvyNKesHIf2hJAyg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">cream</a> is the best of the best! I use this nightly (with a few of <a href="https://rstyle.me/+wt1pU8gVA3NxWuw-zyHNBg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">my favorite tanning drops</a> mixed in) and this keeps my skin from getting chapped during the winter!</p>
<p>You can get these minis in a <a href="https://rstyle.me/+S9ChQFiFGB1OuzmHAzGL5g" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">stocking-stuffer-sized duo</a> and save $6 + use my code &#8216;TARA&#8217; for 20% off you entire purchase!</p>
<h3><strong><a href="https://rstyle.me/+keag4iH3haEyrRRI3UssQQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Tone</a></strong></h3>
<p>I used to think I had to use a toner every single night, but the truth is, it just kept drying out my skin! But with TULA&#8217;s <a href="https://rstyle.me/+keag4iH3haEyrRRI3UssQQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">pro-glycolic 10% ph resurfacing gel</a>, it simply  sloughs off dead skin cells (without over-drying), removes impurities, diminishes the appearance of pores after cleansing, deeply hydrates and conditions the skin for more radiance and glow. In fact:</p>
<h4>&#8220;97% OF WOMEN SAID THEIR SKIN FELT MORE HYDRATED AFTER USING THIS <a href="https://rstyle.me/+keag4iH3haEyrRRI3UssQQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">RESURFACING GEL</a> AS THEIR TONER STEP FOR 4 WEEKS. THE MAJORITY OF WOMEN AGREED THEIR SKIN TONE LOOKED MORE EVEN AND THEIR SKIN FELT SOFTER, SMOOTHER, AND PLUMPER.&#8221;</h4>
<p><a href="https://rstyle.me/+keag4iH3haEyrRRI3UssQQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><img class="wp-image-9264 size-large aligncenter" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/us_tula_phgel-min_1024x-824x1024.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="795" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/us_tula_phgel-min_1024x-824x1024.jpg 824w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/us_tula_phgel-min_1024x-242x300.jpg 242w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/us_tula_phgel-min_1024x-768x954.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/us_tula_phgel-min_1024x.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
<p>Used directly after cleansing on dry, clean skin, this toner is one of the major steps in locking in moisture!</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>SHOP ALL MY TULA FAVORITES</strong></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><div class="shopthepost-widget" data-widget-id="3843765">
