                </div>
            </div></p>
<h3><strong><a href="https://rstyle.me/+XdYloYYt1qEYNYiqTVtC8Q" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Don&#8217;t Forget Your Eyes</a></strong></h3>
<p>I don&#8217;t know about you but my eyes can get crepey and dried out during the winter months. It&#8217;s not a pretty site! But I love TULA&#8217;s new <a href="https://rstyle.me/+XdYloYYt1qEYNYiqTVtC8Q" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">rose glow &amp; get it cooling &amp; brightening eye balm</a>. Made with the same probiotics + superfoods in their <a href="https://rstyle.me/+6haB07xMvlXtpls_PxufqA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">original Eye Balm</a> (think: caffeine, aloe, blueberry &amp; hyaluronic acid), plus the addition of rosehip oil (a plant-based retinol alternative) &amp; hydrating rosewater so you feel instantly energized, awake &amp; ready to glow.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9181" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09794.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09794.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09794-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09794-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09794-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9178" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09797.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09797.jpg 6000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09797-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09797-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09797-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>You can see the glow on my arm straight away and it does exactly that when applied on the undereye! It instantly hydrates, cools, and almost reflects light so that even if you&#8217;re not resting well, your eyes won&#8217;t tattle on you!</p>
<h3><a href="https://rstyle.me/+s_4ECLFqt6xdsydQhXDQOw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><strong>Mask On Mask Off</strong></a></h3>
<p>When it comes to my skincare routine, the most indulgent thing I do is mask once or twice a week. In my opinion, there&#8217;s no better form of beauty T.L.C. than devoting 20 to 30 minutes to take care of your skin. And <a href="https://rstyle.me/+s_4ECLFqt6xdsydQhXDQOw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">face masks</a> are designed to deliver high concentrations of active ingredients to your skin than almost anything else out there!</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9183" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09805.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09805.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09805-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09805-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09805-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>I love this <a href="https://rstyle.me/+s_4ECLFqt6xdsydQhXDQOw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">hydrogel mask</a> for a number of reasons because it has so many dang benefits:</p>
<ul>
<li>Calms distressed skin and relieves the look of redness and inflammation</li>
<li>Brightens the appearance of skin</li>
<li>Improves the look of skin elasticity</li>
<li>Contains probiotics and superfoods for a truly healthy glow</li>
<li>Aids moisture retention</li>
</ul>
<p>It&#8217;s these 6 products that are getting me through this dry winter and when you snag all 6, you get MAJOR savings!</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9180" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804.jpg 6000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC09804-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://rstyle.me/+U_YCW7CPh97daslFQ3Yiuw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">GLOW ALL OUT KIT</a></strong></h3>
<p>When you purchase the <a href="https://rstyle.me/+U_YCW7CPh97daslFQ3Yiuw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Glow All Out Kit</a>, you get:</p>
<ul>
