<li>rose glow &amp; get it cooling &amp; brightening eye balm (0.35oz)</li>
<li>limited edition rose gold cosmetic bag</li>
</ul>
<p>For $98! <a href="https://rstyle.me/+U_YCW7CPh97daslFQ3Yiuw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">This 5-star kit</a> is valued at $174.00 and you&#8217;re getting $76 savings! But make sure you use my code TARA to get an additional 20% off your purchase!</p>
<p>Winter came, but that doesn&#8217;t mean your skin has to suffer!</p>
