				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The truth? I am wearing a pimple patch right now. And regardless of when you read this blog post, I will most likely be wearing a pimple patch. Why? Because they&#8217;re thin, flesh-colored, and barely noticeable. So not noticeable, in fact, that while most people just wear them to bed, I forget about them completely and have been known to make pimple patches a 24-hour situation.</p>
<p>And it&#8217;s because they WORK! My love of pimple patching runs about as deep as my love of Nerds Jelly Beans, pink shimmery eyeshadow, and shoes. That&#8217;s a LOT of love. So when <a href="https://rstyle.me/+a_GogF1BCPHvI5drKyhPLA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Soko Glam</a> (the maker of the famous <a href="https://rstyle.me/+symDjMvOOjB4T2zwHpFr_A" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Acne Pimple Master Patch</a> reached out to me to share some of my favorite things, I screamed, &#8220;YES!&#8221; (just kidding, I typed it politely in an email, but my excitement level was the same)</p>
<p>So here they are, my picks from <a href="https://rstyle.me/+a_GogF1BCPHvI5drKyhPLA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Soko Glam</a> that should be on every one of your lists as stocking stuffers this year! (To quote Julie Andrews, these are a few of my favorite things.)</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9047" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00838_1.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00838_1.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00838_1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00838_1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00838_1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://rstyle.me/+NPbqXcM0XvZvGOOqWnLqbQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">REFINING PEEL GEL</a> | <a href="https://rstyle.me/+T_GyJ_Fk04pwq0yhqaLV5Q" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">LIP SLEEP MASK</a> | <a href="https://rstyle.me/+txA5FYtH2JVQJuXAnIF-FQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">TRIPLE C</a> | <a href="https://rstyle.me/+AFgTl5VmZ6M_uo3FRZC-5g" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">SKINRX MADECERA</a> | <a href="https://rstyle.me/+rVu4dkUrASwBfD04temwOA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">BIO-PEEL GAUZE</a> | <a href="https://rstyle.me/+E-liDVH3GVO7uPVeBsUejw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">CLEAN IT ZERO</a></p>
<h3><a href="https://rstyle.me/+symDjMvOOjB4T2zwHpFr_A" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><strong>#1 ACNE PIMPLE MASTER PATCH</strong></a></h3>
<p>Yes, I mentioned them above but let me tell you a little bit more about WHY I love these babies so much and why next time you&#8217;re tempted to pop and pick your blemishes you should slap a <a href="https://rstyle.me/+symDjMvOOjB4T2zwHpFr_A" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">pimple patch</a> on top of it.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9057" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00917_1.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00917_1.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00917_1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00917_1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00917_1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /> <div class="flex_row col-2"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9045" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00909_1.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00909_1.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00909_1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00909_1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00909_1-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9054" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00822_1.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00822_1.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00822_1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00822_1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00822_1-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></div></p>
<p>Unlike some spot treatments, <a href="https://rstyle.me/+symDjMvOOjB4T2zwHpFr_A" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">this patch</a> won&#8217;t leave your skin dry and flaky. The hydrocolloid circles cling to skin no matter where you end up wearing them. Despite their staying power, they&#8217;re still easy and pain-free to peel off. They also come in three different sizes depending on what kind of coverage you need. You&#8217;ll know it&#8217;s working because you can see the process happening: The clear patch turns white and expands, and the skin (where your zit once was) flattens out and becomes redness-free. After a couple of hours (or a good night&#8217;s sleep), you&#8217;ll forget you had one to begin with!</p>
<p>And if that isn&#8217;t convincing enough, if you&#8217;re a picker, these are about to become your best friend! These will provide a barrier between your fresh wound and your grabby little paws. Picking is the worst and the chances of scarring and getting an infection rise. With all this in mind, you should slip <a href="https://rstyle.me/+symDjMvOOjB4T2zwHpFr_A" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">some of these</a> into your stocking as well!</p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong>SHOP ALL SOKO ACNE PATCHES</strong></h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><div class="shopthepost-widget" data-widget-id="3836979">
