<h3><a href="https://rstyle.me/+NPbqXcM0XvZvGOOqWnLqbQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><strong>#2 SATURDAY SKIN Rub-A-Dub Refining Peel Gel</strong></a></h3>
<p>Since I purchased the majority of these items to go into my girl&#8217;s stockings, I wanted to make sure I was getting them basics but also items that are super gentle and would help them build great skincare habits early on! I wanted to avoid the supermarket exfoliators full of ingredients that are harsh and cause micro-tears in the skin. Instead, I opted for <a href="https://rstyle.me/+NPbqXcM0XvZvGOOqWnLqbQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">this gel</a> that&#8217;s gentle enough for my teen&#8217;s skin and simple enough that my girls would actually use it once a week.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9055" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00828_1.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00828_1.jpg 1000w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00828_1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00828_1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00828_1-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /> <div class="flex_row col-2"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9053" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00833_1.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00833_1.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00833_1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00833_1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00833_1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9050" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00837_1.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00837_1.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00837_1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00837_1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00837_1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /></div></p>
<p>Instead of a physical scrub or chemical exfoliator, this <a href="https://rstyle.me/+NPbqXcM0XvZvGOOqWnLqbQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">peel gel</a> removes dead skin cells and buildup with natural enzymes like papaya and bromelain (found in pineapple) and 100% Ecocert Certified cellulose for a bright and smooth, not sensitized, complexion. And watching it work is pretty cool! As you rub the <a href="https://rstyle.me/+NPbqXcM0XvZvGOOqWnLqbQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">gel</a> into your skin, you can actually see all the yucky stuff clump up!</p>
<p>Another treat I picked up are the <a href="https://rstyle.me/+rVu4dkUrASwBfD04temwOA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Neogen Bio-Peel Gauze Exfoliating Pads</a>. Many exfoliants can be too harsh on sensitive skin, but <a href="https://rstyle.me/+rVu4dkUrASwBfD04temwOA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">these pads</a> have over 800 positive reviews for a reason. It comes with 30 single-use pads that prompt a chemical exfoliation process to remove dead skin, clogged pores, and makeup residue, all without causing issues. I actually plan on keeping <a href="https://rstyle.me/+rVu4dkUrASwBfD04temwOA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">these bad boys</a> for myself!</p>
<h3><a href="https://rstyle.me/+txA5FYtH2JVQJuXAnIF-FQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><strong>#3 Triple C Lightning Liquid &#8211; Vitamin C Serum</strong></a></h3>
<p>There&#8217;s a reason <a href="https://rstyle.me/+txA5FYtH2JVQJuXAnIF-FQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">this powerhouse</a> made it on my list and a must for me and my girls! <a href="https://rstyle.me/+txA5FYtH2JVQJuXAnIF-FQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Triple C Lightning Liquid</a> is a vitamin C serum that helps lighten brown spots and even out your skin tone. This one has made every <a href="https://rstyle.me/+FprQ0o1xF8vd4ujAliLBJw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">best-of skincare</a> list and sold out within 4 hours when it originally launched! It also works wonders on sunspots, acne scars, and melasma.</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9043" src="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00840_1.jpg" alt="" width="2250" height="1500" srcset="https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00840_1.jpg 2250w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00840_1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00840_1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://tarathueson.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DSC00840_1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2250px) 100vw, 2250px" /></p>
<p>Another thing I love about <a href="https://rstyle.me/+txA5FYtH2JVQJuXAnIF-FQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">this serum</a> is that it&#8217;s made in small batches to ensure its effectiveness! From Soko: &#8221; In order for a pure vitamin C serum to be effective, it must be fresh. That&#8217;s why we&#8217;re making all <a href="https://rstyle.me/+txA5FYtH2JVQJuXAnIF-FQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Triple C Lightning Liquids</a> in small batches and air shipping them directly from Korea to ensure that the serums are fresh and high quality. To maximize the effectiveness of your serum, it&#8217;s best to store it in the refrigerator or a cool, dark place. Keep the bottle airtight!&#8221;</p>
<p>These are the 3 main things I plan on sticking in stockings this year but Soko Glam has a ton of other products that make headlines and <a href="https://rstyle.me/+FprQ0o1xF8vd4ujAliLBJw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">best-of lists</a> everywhere because of their modern approach to beauty and their incredible results!</p>
