				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Don&#8217;t you just hate how difficult it is to plan ahead for <strong>Black Friday</strong> and <strong>Cyber Monday sales</strong>? Even though everything&#8217;s mostly online these days, all the details stay shrouded in secrecy until the last minute, leaving you as stressed as you would have been jockeying for position during a good old-fashioned mall stampede. I honestly just wish Black Friday could be spent like Goldie below!</p>
