<p>But if you&#8217;re determined to get some shopping done, might I suggest you stay cozy and warm in your home and do it online? I don&#8217;t understand why more people don&#8217;t do this! And thankfully, <b>I have decided to help you out</b> and lower your collective heart rates this year by rounding up my favorite stores and what sales they have for Black Friday! (Insert sigh of relief here.)</p>
