<p style="text-align: left;">4) <a href="https://rstyle.me/+ObPTy7a5lu1W71enUJkUVQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Amazon 2-pack Echo Show 5 w/ Smart Display and Alexa</a> &#8211; (Over $500 separately)</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">5) <a href="https://rstyle.me/+HHaO3WE1hL-Ewb3-XBNeJQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">In The Wild Leopard Barefoot Dreams Blanket</a> &#8211; $126.00 (normally $180)</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">6) <a href="https://rstyle.me/+z-rB2QzgyXSH3KbaUMFBAw" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">TULA 25% OFF sale</a> &#8211; <b>25% OFF </b>all orders on TULA.com from Nov 28 &#8211; Dec 1 with Discount Code <b>BLACKFRIDAY19</b></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">7) <a href="https://rstyle.me/+zrc4rNQHC6i1wHtrQz1FNA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Barefoot Dreams CozyChic<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Hooded Zip Robe</a> &#8211; $96.60 (normally $138)</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">8) <a href="https://rstyle.me/+MfrdfWNsZrsvYCJNgRNWfQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Adidas SenseBoosts</a> &#8211; $84 (normally $120 and the best shoes I&#8217;ve ever owned!)</p>
